all players]]\n[[Category:Denver Broncos players]]\n\n* [[Duke Blue Devils football]] :\n** Earned 1976 All-America Honors as the [[Center (football)]]<ref name=\":0\" />\n** Won the [[Atlantic Coast Conference]] [[Jacobs Blocking Trophy]]<ref name=\":0\" /> \n* [[Denver Broncos]]<ref name=\":0\" />\n** Participated in 4 [[Super Bowl]]'s<ref name=\":0\" />\n** [[All-Pro]] in 1985\n** 13 seasons in the [[National Football League]]<ref name=\":0\" /><br />\n{{offensive-lineman-1950s-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Jsoroka1108", "label": "safe", "comment": "added a bit about his professional career and statistics", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Billy_Bryan"}
